- ❌ Missing: Intent definition / determinism definition
- ❌ Missing: Mathematical formula + calculus
- ❌ Missing: Lemmas + invariants
- ❌ Missing: Notebook evidence + artifact export
- ❌ Missing: Green scorecard gate

